    GLfloat col[4] = {gc->fr, gc->fg, gc->fb, gc->fa};
    glWrapper->Uniform4fv(gr->color_location, 1, col);
}
```

Now, use Google Mock to mock the `GLWrapperInterface` and write a test for `set_color`.

